      <guid>/en/blog/fora_da_politica/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Participation in the edition &lt;a href=&#34;https://foradapoliticanaohasalvacao.blog/2024/09/16/eleicoes-brasil-afora-com-lucas-gelape-marco-antonio-faganello-239/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Elections across Brazil | 239&lt;/a&gt; of the podcast &lt;a href=&#34;https://foradapoliticanaohasalvacao.blog/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Fora da política não há salvação&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, produced by &lt;a href=&#34;https://eaesp.fgv.br/pessoa/claudio-goncalves-couto&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Cláudio Couto&lt;/a&gt;, alongside colleague &lt;a href=&#34;http://lattes.cnpq.br/7299940252994768&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Marco Antonio Faganello&lt;/a&gt; (FGV-CEPESP).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The interview discussed how Political Science helps to understand municipal elections, especially the 2024 race.&lt;/p&gt;

